# 📝 NoteVault – Secure Notes App (Flask + JSON)

NoteVault is a full-stack web application built using Python (Flask) and HTML/CSS/JS that allows users to sign up, log in, and securely manage their personal notes. It is simple, lightweight, and mobile-friendly — ideal for beginners learning frontend and backend integration.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 User Signup & Login system
- 📝 Add, view, and save personal notes
- 💾 Notes stored securely using JSON files
- 📱 Mobile-responsive design
- 🧠 Easy-to-read and modular Flask code
- 💡 Beginner-friendly project for learning full stack development

